    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 You have got to see this beauty! It is in absolutely stunning condition\u2014honestly, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I have taken such good care of it, keeping it waxed and tucked away in the garage, so there isn't a scratch or a smudge to be found. It drives like an absolute dream and is ready for a new home. If you're looking for perfection at a fair price, this is your lucky day! Come take it for a spin and see for yourself! \u2728",
