    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six with its high-revving 8,000 RPM redline and individual throttle bodies. This example is mechanically pristine, with the critical rod bearing service and VANOS solenoid overhaul recently completed. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission delivers crisp, tactile engagement, paired with a factory-spec limited-slip differential for optimal torque vectoring. The chassis is structurally flawless, showing no signs of the common rear subframe fatigue. Finished in Carbon Black over Nappa leather, the exterior retains its factory luster with zero panel gaps or oxidation. A true driver's machine with a comprehensive service history, ready for the most discerning collector.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
