    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly museum-grade 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera 4S in Arctic Silver Metallic over Graphite Grey full leather. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, showing no signs of age or road wear. The exterior paint retains its factory-deep luster with zero swirl marks, stone chips, or imperfections; it has been treated with a multi-layer ceramic coating for lasting protection. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom state\u2014the leather is supple with no bolster wear, the original carpets are pristine, and every switchgear operates with a crisp, mechanical precision. Mechanically, this Porsche is beyond reproach. It comes with a binder of comprehensive service records from day one, including the proactive replacement of the IMS bearing and rear main seal. The undercarriage is as clean as the body, showing no corrosion or fluid leaks. The original Turbo-look wheels are free of curb rash and are wrapped in fresh, N-rated Michelin Pilot Sport tires. This is an investment-grade example for the discerning collector who demands perfection.",
      "price": 43900.0,
